Hey there, I'm Pranav, your go-to athlete for a good laugh on the squash court. I may be new to the game, but trust me, my swings are nothing short of avant-garde. When it comes to table tennis and badminton, well, let's just say my skills are an acquired taste – like fine art, you have to appreciate the uniqueness.

In squash, I've mastered the art of hitting the ball everywhere except where it's supposed to go. Table tennis and badminton are my playgrounds for creating gravity-defying shots that even I can't predict. If you're looking for a wildcard with a knack for turning every match into a comedy show, bid on me. I may not win, but I guarantee you'll be thoroughly entertained!
